\begin_inset Formula $\mathbf{z}$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $\hat{\mathbf{z}}$
\end_inset

,
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{align}
D_{z} & =\left(\mathbf{z}-\hat{\mathbf{z}}\right)^{T}\left(\mathbf{z}-\hat{\mathbf{z}}\right)\nonumber \\
 & =2-2\mathbf{z}^{T}\hat{\mathbf{z}}\ .\label{eq:distance-Dz}
\end{align}

\end_inset

We can then rewrite 
