reference "eq:distance_v1"

\end_inset

 as
\begin_inset Formula 
\begin{equation}
D=\left(g-\hat{g}\right)^{2}+g\hat{g}D_{z}\ ,\label{eq:pvq_distortion}
\end{equation}

\end_inset

which separates the gain quantization from the quantization of the unit
 vector 
